* John Stride as Tom Shepard, Captain Shepard&#x27;s son, TAG (Telegraphist/Air Gunner) in &quot;Ark Royal&quot;&#x27;s Swordfish squadron (uncredited)
* Donald Churchill as Seaman on &quot;Ark Royal&quot; (uncredited)
