* &quot;Love Child&quot;, by Swing Out Sister from &quot;Get in Touch with Yourself&quot;, 1992
* &quot;Lovechild&quot;, by Talisman from &quot;Genesis&quot;, 1993

==Other media==
* &quot;Love Child&quot; (TV series), a 2014–2017 Australian drama series
